	<strong>Description</strong></p>
<p>
	We are looking for a Software Configuration Manager to be responsible for collaborating with multiple teams on configuration management, build, and release activities. The primary development and build platform is Microsoft Windows Server 2008 with related technologies including .Net 4, IIS 7, Team Foundation Server 2010, Visual Studio 2010, and SQL Server 2008. This position will provide guidance and implement Software Configuration Management (SCM), source code branching, merging, build strategies and deployment strategies along with maintaining the tools and environments to help the teams deliver major software releases.<br />
	&nbsp;</p>
